OL,3,CLack of support leaves mother, 78,
OL,4,Ccaring for bedbound son
OL,6,FA 78-year-old mother in Jersey says
OL,7,Fshe has to provide constant care for
OL,8,Fher bedbound son, who has motor
OL,9,Fneurone disease (MND), due to a lack
OL,10,Fof support.
OL,12,FKevin Harding, 56, was diagnosed with
OL,13,Fthe muscle-wasting condition four
OL,14,Fyears ago and only gets limited
OL,15,Fgovernment help - leaving his elderly
OL,16,Fmother, who has health problems of her
OL,17,Fown, to look after him the rest of the
OL,18,Ftime.
