OL,3,CLack of support leaves mother, 78,
OL,4,Ccaring for bedbound son
OL,6,FKevin, a former chef and keen
OL,7,Fsportsman, is now reliant on round-the-
OL,8,Fclock care to live.
OL,10,FHe says: "I have a problem with
OL,11,Fchoking that comes at any point. If
OL,12,Fsomeone's not near me, I can't breathe.
OL,14,F"I can't move my arms or my legs and
OL,15,Fif I've got an itch anywhere, I can't
OL,16,Fitch it.
OL,18,F"It's hard work for my mother, she's
OL,19,Fnot young."
