OL,3,CLack of support leaves mother, 78,
OL,4,Ccaring for bedbound son
OL,6,FSusan Harding, 78, says a lack of care
OL,7,Fprovision means she cannot leave her
OL,8,Fson's side and has not been able to
OL,9,Ffor the last four months, despite
OL,10,Fneeding to attend to her own health
OL,11,Fneeds.
OL,13,FShe explains: "You can't sit down and
OL,14,Frelax ... Kevin gets pain every day
OL,15,Fand you have to move his limbs to ease
OL,16,Fthat.
OL,18,F"You don't get help when you
OL,19,Fdesperately need it ... it would be
OL,20,Fhelpful if we could have that help and
OL,21,Fnot have to fight for it."
