OL,3,CLack of support leaves mother, 78,
OL,4,Ccaring for bedbound son
OL,6,FSusan says she is limited by the
OL,7,Fgovernment's quota of allotted hours
OL,8,Fof support, which does not give her
OL,9,Fenough time to do anything for
OL,10,Fherself, including attending her own
OL,11,Fdoctor appointments and vaccinations.
OL,13,FShe adds: "It's quite disgraceful
OL,14,Freally, for the time and the help we
OL,15,Fneed. I'm saving them money looking
OL,16,Fafter Kevin."
