OL,3,CLack of support leaves mother, 78,
OL,4,Ccaring for bedbound son
OL,6,FKevin also urges the Government to do
OL,7,Fmore, saying: "Give people who need 24-
OL,8,Fhour care as much dignity as possible
OL,9,Fand as much enjoyment as they can, for
OL,10,Fas long as they can."
OL,12,FThere are currently around 25 people
OL,13,Fin the Channel Islands known to have
OL,14,FMND, with a life expectancy from
OL,15,Fdiagnosis of two to three years on
OL,16,Faverage.
